{
 "name": "RPlog_Nothing_Goes_As_Planned",
 "title": "Nothing Goes as Planned",
 "summary": "In the warehouse outskirts of New Alderaan, the disguised Imperial agent Rainer lures Senator Tokoga to a clandestine meeting, ostensibly to introduce him to dangerous people, while the medic Myiari watches from a hidden alley. The trap springs as Rainer reveals he means to capture the Senator and Myiari is herself ambushed at gunpoint by Brek, who is working with Rainer. A vicious brawl erupts between Myiari and Brek even as Tokoga tries to turn his hold-out blaster against Rainer, and stormtroopers close in. Despite the prisoners' resistance, Tokoga is beaten down and Myiari is disarmed and subdued, the Imperials securing both captives as their carefully laid plan, however messily, succeeds.",
